test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 76 == -76
 +  where 76 = <built-in function prod>([-76, -1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (1 == 3)
 +  where 1 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7f566c3e7440>([-76])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7f566c3e7440> = [[-76, 1, -76], [-76], [-76, 1, -76], [-76, 1]].count
